Energy Act of 2008, referred to in subsec. (d)(3)(A), probably means ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246/s14008"},"text":"section 14008 of Pub. L. 110–246","children":[],"tail":", which is set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s2279"},"text":"section 2279 of this title","children":[],"tail":", because section 14008 of the Act established the Advisory Committee on Minority Farmers and section 14009 of the Act amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s7000"},"text":"section 7000 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The date of the enactment of this section, referred to in subsec. (d)(4)(B), is the date of enactment of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–246","children":[],"tail":", which was approved "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-06-18"},"text":"June 18, 2008","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 5(b) of the Agricultural Credit Improvement Act of 1992, referred to in subsec. (e)(2)(C), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/554/s5/b"},"text":"section 5(b) of Pub. L. 102–554","children":[],"tail":", which is set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1929"},"text":"section 1929 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"ideff4140c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/234"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–234","children":[],"tail":" and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–246","children":[],"tail":" enacted identical sections. "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/234"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–234","children":[],"tail":" was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246/s4/a"},"text":"section 4(a) of Pub. L. 110–246","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"ideff4140d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2018—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/334/s12406/a/1/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–334, § 12406(a)(1)(A)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Partnerships and Public Engagement” for “Advocacy and Outreach” in section catchline."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/334/s12406/a/1/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–334, § 12406(a)(1)(B)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Partnerships and Public Engagement” for “Advocacy and Outreach”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/334/s12406/a/1/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–334, § 12406(a)(1)(B)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Partnerships and Public Engagement” for “Advocacy and Outreach” in introductory provisions."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b)(1)(B)(iv), (v), (C). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/334/s12406/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–334, § 12406(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", added cls. (iv) and (v) of subpar. (B) and subpar. (C)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/334/s12406/b/2/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–334, § 12406(b)(2)(A)","children":[],"tail":", inserted “veteran farmers and ranchers,” after “beginning farmers or ranchers,” in introductory provisions."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/334/s12406/b/2/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–334, § 12406(b)(2)(B)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “socially disadvantaged, or veteran” for “or socially disadvantaged”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c)(5). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/334/s12406/b/2/C"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–334, § 12406(b)(2)(C)","children":[],"tail":", inserted “veteran farmers or ranchers,” after “beginning farmers or ranchers,”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d)(4)(B). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/334/s12406/a/1/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–334, § 12406(a)(1)(B)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Partnerships and Public Engagement” for “Advocacy and Outreach”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (e)(2)(B). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/334/s12406/a/2/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–334, § 12406(a)(2)(A)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “the beginning farmer and rancher development grant program established under subsection (d) of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s2279"},"text":"section 2279 of this title","children":[],"tail":".” for “the beginning farmer and rancher development program established under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s3319f"},"text":"section 3319f of this title","children":[],"tail":".”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (f)(3)(B). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/334/s12406/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–334, § 12406(c)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “2023” for “2018”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2014—Subsec. (f)(3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/79"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–79","children":[],"tail":" amended par. (3) generally. Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “There are authorized to be appropriated such sums as are necessary to carry out this subsection for each of fiscal years 2009 through 2012.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes"